---
title: Sizzling Hoisin Shrimp with Ginger Scallion Rice & Crispy Green Beans
description: If you’re like us, you’ve seen a lot of stir-fries in your day. But thanks to our sweet hoisin shrimp marinade, aromatic rice, and a sprinkle of nutty sesame seeds, this one is bound to top them all. It cooks super-quickly and brings a tour de force of Asian-style flavors that even the pickiest of eaters will love. Sounds like a win-win to us.
